---
import Section from "../layouts/Section.astro";
import Title from "../layouts/Titles.astro";
---

<Section id="reco">
  <Title >Recommendation</Title>
  <div class="pt-20">
    <div
      class="w-full max-w-64 mx-auto px-3 py-4 text-gray-800 bg-white rounded-lg shadow-lg dark:bg-gray-800 dark:text-gray-50"
    >
      <div class="w-full pt-1 mx-auto -mt-16 text-center flex flex-row">
        <a
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/francisco-cogollo/"
          class="relative block"
          target="_blank"
        >
          <img
            alt="profil"
            src="https://scontent-bog2-2.xx.fbcdn.net/v/t1.6435-1/198666325_10159645844778120_270851975132882564_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_p200x200&_nc_cat=109&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=2b6aad&_nc_eui2=AeEIfkFDqI4iPsBQraCSDATvwAvE3IRzUF_AC8TchHNQXwMgua2Ye65SeUPYH4m0hWg&_nc_ohc=i8NrgDyof8UAX_lHawS&_nc_ht=scontent-bog2-2.xx&oh=00_AfB_utIHeIrhNg0yghTici_vE4D8dyo4ZOOdEb2ge09hDA&oe=66043C17"
            class="mx-auto object-cover rounded-full h-20 w-20"
          />
        </a>
        <div>
          <span
            class="bg-blue-100 text-blue-800 text-xs font-medium me-2 px-2.5 py-0.5 rounded-full dark:bg-blue-900 dark:text-blue-300"
            >linkedin</span
          >
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="w-full">
        <div class="mb-1 text-center md:text-left max-w-60">
          <p
            class="text-xl text-center md:text-left font-medium text-gray-800 dark:text-white"
          >
            Fransisco Cogollo
          </p>
          <p class="text-xs text-blue-700 dark:text-[#7e5aff] font-semibold text-center md:text-left">
            Lead DevOps Engineer @EPAM Systems
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <p class="text-xl text-justify md:text-2xl pt-4">
      I had the pleasure of collaborating with Jaime on an EKS project, and it
      was a remarkable experience. His profound knowledge of AWS, especially in
      EKS, is truly praiseworthy. Jaime not only showcased strong technical
      skills but also made complex concepts easily understandable. His
      collaborative approach, dedication to continuous learning, and positive
      attitude significantly enhanced our team dynamics. I believe his expertise
      and easy-going nature make him a valuable asset for any AWS-related
      endeavors.
    </p>
  </div>
</Section>
